<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201021/3a7efe718d4742b38385c7573ceb82a7.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">教堂内部</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201021/466d148bc845497c8ee2c068a17a6aed.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">教堂内部</span></img></p>
